@startuml
state "User Not Registered" as UserNotRegistered
state "User Registered" as UserRegistered
state "Video Watching" as VideoWatching
state "Video Uploading" as VideoUploading
state "Likes List" as LikesList
state "Discussion Option" as DiscussionOption

[*] --> UserNotRegistered
UserNotRegistered --> UserRegistered : create account
UserRegistered --> [*]
UserRegistered --> VideoUploading : upload video
VideoUploading --> UserRegistered : upload complete
UserRegistered --> VideoWatching : watch video
VideoWatching --> LikesList : save to likes list
LikesList --> UserRegistered : view saved videos
UserRegistered --> DiscussionOption : enter discussion option

@enduml
